<h4 align="Left" style="color: seagreen">What do we do?</h4>
<p>Now we are an e-commerce platform that serves to connect hundreds of artisans around the globe with an interested audience, in a way that is easily accessible, secure, fun and hip. This is what Mr Khumalo wanted all along. He was the man with dream...</p>
