<h4 align="Left" style="color: seagreen">Why do we do it?</h4>
<p>Why do we do what we do? Because why not? There is no other e-commerce platform such as us! We are the first international platform to allow artisans from anywhere in the world to showcase their beautiful art by reaching a global audience. We do it because we're passionate about uniting truly talented artisans out there with people that would truly appreciate their craftmanship and then allowing said people to show their appreciation of the artisan's work with the ability to even purchase the art and thus, compensate the artisan for their valiant effort. We are KhumaloCraft! There is nothing we cannot bring into fruition when it comes to art! Art really does bring people closer!</p>
